#include<stdio.h>
#include<stdlib.h>

int cmpfunc(const void *a, const void *b){
	return(*(int *)a - *(int *)b);
}

int main(){
	int t, n; scanf("%d", &t);
	while(t-- && scanf("%d", &n)){
		int a[n], i, m, f = 0;
		for(i = 0; i < n; scanf("%d", &a[i++]));
		qsort(a, n, sizeof(int), cmpfunc), m = a[0];
		for(i = 1; i < n; i++){
			if(a[i] <= m){f = 1, printf("NO\n"); break;}
			m = a[i];
		}
		if(f == 0)	printf("YES\n");
	}		
	return 0;
}
